Program: Free Thinking
Title: John Boorman
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b05yl1wb
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 29 Mar 2016
Director John Boorman talks to Matthew Sweet about his most recent film Queen and Country and its place in one of the most distinguished careers in British cinema history - a career that embraces Excalibur, Deliverance and Point Blank as well as Hope and Glory. Producer: Zahid Warley First broadcast last year. Show less